message.name: ERR_AES_LOGICALLY_EQUIVALENT_CONFIG_RULE_PARSE_FAILURE
message.locale: The logically equivalent configuration's XML rule could not be parsed.

message.name: ERR_AES_ACTIVATION_FAILURE_DUE_TO_DELIVERYPLAN_IN_RESILIENCE_MODE

message.name: ERR_AES_MISSING_MANDATORY_DATA
message.locale: The incoming evidence cannot be added to this case because there is a problem with the evidence information. Edit the incoming evidence to correct the information and try again.

message.name: ERR_AES_MISSING_MANDATORY_DATA_MULTI
message.locale: The incoming evidence cannot be added to this case because there is a problem with the evidence information. Edit each incoming evidence record in the timeline to correct the information and try again.
